description: Triggers the website-audit skill when user asks to audit, verify, QA, or check a website after creation
globs: src/websites/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

When the user asks to audit, verify, QA, or check a website:

1. Read and follow `.cursor/skills/website-audit/SKILL.md`
2. Also follow `.cursor/skills/atlagia-ecommerce-frontend/SKILL.md` for design and style rules
3. Use MCP browser verification at every step — do NOT skip screenshots
4. Fix every problem before advancing to the next step
5. Never modify core files — fixes go in `src/websites/<StoreName>/` only
